The main topics of the study of steel:

- The principle of operation and device of ground drones. The concept of nrtk;

- analysis of emergency situations;

- areas of use of NRTK in the zone of the SV;

- visual piloting NRTK (free riding, riding a point of interest, snake and mirror ride);

- piloting NRTK on the FPV camera (snake, riding on the labyrinth, free riding);

- NRTK piloting with adjustment (accompaniment) from the DJI MAVIC 3 drone along the route (imitation of mining of a truck, passage over the bridge to the pipe, discharge of cargo - food, ammunition to the unit, return home).
At the moment, in the zone of their ground drones, they are increasingly showing their demand and effectiveness. They help our fighters deliver various cargoes, cleanse the passages, distract the enemy fire on themselves, are used as kamikaze. Therefore, acquaintance with terrestrial drones is an important component of the preparation of the instructor composition of the direction ‚ÄúApplication of unmanned systems‚Äù of the Center ‚ÄúWarrior‚Äù.

